<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.7">
<l>miṭaiyā vanta vēlmaṉṉar vīya vicayaṉ tērkaṭavi</l>
<l>kuṭaiyā varaiyoṉ ṟeṭuttāyar kōvāy niṉṟāṉ kūrāḻip</l>
<l>paṭaiyāṉ vētam nāṉkaintu vēḷvi yaṅka māṟicaiyēḻ</l>
<l>naṭaiyā valla vantaṇarvāḻ naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who, having driven Vijaya’s chariot to destroy lance[-bearing] kings</l>
<l rend="indent">who came, swarming [together],</l>
<l>Stood as the herder king bearing a mountain as an umbrella,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one with the sharp discus weapon,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where dwell priests</l>
<l rend="indent">who have properly mastered</l>
<l>The four Vedas, five sacrifices, six branches [of knowledge],</l>
<l rend="indent">and seven musical modes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
